#This is a client/server model socket programming(based on zmq) where client requests server of the weather details from api.weathermap.org OWM. The REST api is curl implementation. The server is multithreaded with the pthread framework

Makefile - needs modification(CFLAGS and LFLAGS) depending on the development environment installation 
Library used: jsoncpp, zmq, curl and pthread

invoking 
./server - preferable as bg process

./client  <message_code> <parameters>
./client 1 <cityid>
         2 <longitude> <latitude>
         3 <cityname>
         4 <zipcode>




